---
title: Glazed Mumbai Tofu & Rapid Rice with Garlic Veggies & Slivered Almonds
description: We’re all for plant-based meals that don’t sacrifice on flavour or satiety, and this one ticks all the boxes! This tofu is gently spiced with Mumbai flavours and tossed in a sweet apricot sauce for mouth-watering goodness. Garlicky veggies and fluffy rice are the perfect accompaniments!

*We’ve replaced the crushed roasted cashews in this recipe with slivered almonds due to local ingredient availability. It’ll be just as delicious, just follow your recipe card!*
